u know. Leg of beef, crop, and - fry, and sometimes - we've had bacon and liver. Been tasty you know. We've had bacon and liver. But we never had no tinned tomatoes. My dad wouldn't have 'em and we - nor would - and we never liked them. So we never bought
 the tins of tomatoes - and that. But we used to have changes like that and - me mother used to buy the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7368700\charrsid12715645 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645  sheep}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7368700\charrsid12715645 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 
s hearts or the beasts hearts and boil it and then it when it was cold, slice it and you had it between your bread. She used to pack me dad - with that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 It sounds as if you had meat most days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 
No. Half of the time, we didn't have it - but we always had - meat for dinner like, something like in the - way of meat you know, stewing meat. And that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Tinned meat ever?
