\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No. Oh a bit 
of corned beef - she - we've had corned beef - and chips. She did used to buy the bit of corned beef, and chips and give us that - and - on a Friday, mostly, and a few - and - she used to - soak peas and boil some peas, we used to have it like that.

