\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No. No. Nor you had tea - tea in saucer. No. My word you was for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Could you choose what you wanted to eat from what was cooked or did you have to eat a bit of everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No. If you didn't like it - well then you'll have to have something else then if you
 don't like that. Or else you'll have to go without it, that's what me mother used to say. Well what do you want? Jam? And of course there were - you can have treacle then on - bread and butter. You know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 From what you say if you left anything they said you would have to have it at the next meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Yes, they said well if you leave -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Did it ever happen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No, I didn't know - not - not - I never knowed them to put it before us again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Were they very upset if you didn't eat everything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Oh they didn't - no, they did - used to be upset about it. Says, you won't have a dinner another day when you come home perhaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 But she softened in the end?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 If there was something on the table you wanted like salt, could you ask 
