\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No. No. Didn't. It was only as I got - we got older. And that, as we went there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Did you go to concerts when you were at school?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Yes. Daybrook Chapel. Front Street Baptist. And other orchestras as were held at school. And that.
