Kings - picture palace higher up where - Woolworth's used to have their sh}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14112074\charrsid12715645 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 
p first. That used to be a dance hall and - and that and picture palace. Went there. Used to go to the pictures there.
