\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Was it a regular thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Yes, only a ha'penny 'til you started work. And when you started work you got three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14112074\charrsid12715645  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 pence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 What did you spend the money on when it was a ha'penny, what could you get for a ha'penny?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Well an everlasting strip. Farthing nib}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14112074\charrsid12715645 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
