\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No, only just - you know, ord}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14112074\charrsid12715645 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
