\insrsid14112074\charrsid12715645 r}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 nold Wake, Sunday for tea, and we used to go - when it were Bulwell Wakes we used to go there. That Sunday.
