\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 1918. Well 
I'd be - very young. That'd be when I was about in - eighteen or nineteen. I should be about eighteen, seventeen, eighteen in those -
