No. We used to go to the theatre, and we used to go to the Empire and Hippodrome. We used to do a lot of that, he was very fond of - of that - entertainment.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 At this stage did you belong to any savings clubs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 All the savings clubs I had was - War Bonds. But I've drawn them out, I've - after we got into out house to ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 When you were first married did you belong to any boot clubs or sick clubs or funeral clubs or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Did you take part in any sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No, no, oh no, we didn't - I didn't take no part in no sport.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Would your husband have done if he'd been at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Well he was a very big footballer and he - was interested in boxing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 But he watched the football did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 He watched footballing. And he used to like to - go to a good boxing match. Very much in that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Did either you or your husband bet on anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Did he disapprove of that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No, he said 
- he always used to say - every man to their - own choice. If they want to bed let 'em have one, so long as they don't go past the limit. That's what he always used to say. I think - when there used to be the Derby - and the - at Doncaster - I think on th
em two special occasions - with being in the factory like - and that - I think they used to - have - have it between them. You know. Sweepstake, yes. Yes, he did, always on them - two big days. And I think most people does sand does now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 The Grand National sometimes.;
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 
Grand National, that's right. I know - I can remember one year - mind you it was after I - I was married and the boy was - getting on nice age, and - I know they - all had something on what - San Sebina, and it came up. San Sabina, 
that was one of the - race horses. And - one or two of 'em had a good win, between 'em. And they all bought their wives something. And them as didn't buy their wives something they gave 'em - they gave 'em some money. And I know this - San Sabina won. It 
w
as a - a real - winner that - that time and - yet I can't go back to the year, but - many people'd know when San Sabina won - that deal in that work. And I know they all - went in the - it together, and it was drawn out, San Sabina. And - it was a very bi
g win that year, I'll never forget that. Oh it were all the - all the talk then. It was a good win, with a - with a lot of people. But never known him on any other occasion. No. Although - he used to - like to have a - go on the cope - on the coupon.

