\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Well I didn't after that one, that was my - my - job. And what they call a 
- a - wind - not a winder, what they called heeling. Well I went round on a big - thing like that. And that, but that was done - for - then - the - our fellows went out and \{BLANK\}
 They brought you so much, and you put on - you put it on this big - thing l
ike, like a big thing like that, you'd think it were a cape but it wasn't you slipped it on, then find your what is it - and then - it went round onto another - it went so far. Well when you stopped your machine - broke it off, and then you used to take i
t off, then went into these skeins, like that, and put it through, then it used to go with the - socks to be - either mended or anything. That's how that used to be done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Would you have preferred another type of occupation?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No, I was quite - satisfied with that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 You didn't have an exact apprenticeship but did you have a sort of training period at Morley}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid16415534\charrsid12715645 \rquote }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 s?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Was it counted as that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No, well - someone - learnt - showed you how to go on with the machine, and how to wind and that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 It didn't take you long from what you said, or were you extra quick at it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 
It just depends, some took to it better than others. And - they used to - used to have bobbins up here, and your spools down there with it on. Well you used to bring
 it up and thread it, used to come through what they called - some lather, soap stuff. Well when you threaded it all up and started machine, it'd run through this white lather, so the men could work it. Always used to say there's the shack}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16415534\charrsid12715645  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 lad, you know wh
en they wanted anything fetching, or any - or sweeping up. Well they used to sweep - all the alleys out where the two frames was, used to sw}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16415534\charrsid12715645 e}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
