\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Did the you feel that the employers and workers had the same interests or different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No, they - about all had alike in them days. The }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16415534\charrsid12715645 \endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645  frame}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16415534\charrsid12715645 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 men you know that were in the frames and - the bosses.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 You think the bosses and the frame}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16415534\charrsid12715645 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
