\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Oh aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 They weren't very different then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No, I don't think there was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid7885863 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 Could the frame}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16415534\charrsid12715645 -}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
