\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6896403 AK  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11173682\charrsid12715645 No. You had to go in for office work then. But - if you went for framework you was a frame}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
